body.p:
When you copy a fragment that contains tracked attribute changes, the following cases are possible:

if you perform the copy operation with Track Changes enabled, all
          the attribute changes in the fragment are accepted;

if you perform the copy operation with Track Changes disabled,
          the fragment holds the attribute changes inside it.

When you paste a fragment that contains tracked attribute changes, the following cases are possible:

if you perform the paste operation with Track Changes enabled,
          the changes are accepted before the paste operation;

if you perform the paste operation with Track Changes disabled,
          the changes are pasted in the document.
